These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, february, april
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, soccer
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Birthday     | december | february    | april   |
| Sport   | badminton  | soccer | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, drawing, board-games
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, satire, scientific
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |       3       |
| Hobby      | sudoku   | board-games  | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | family | scientific    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-3::.
There 3 different types of food: lime, mango, plum
3 different pets are kept: hamster, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
2. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
3. the person eating lime is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Food   | mango | plum | lime |
| Pet           | mouse    | rat     | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-4::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, rat, dog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, soccer
1. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
4. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Pet    | dog | bird     | rat   |
| Sport   | golf   | biathlon | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-5::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, july, april
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, trike
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the trike is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Birthday   | july | february | april   |
| Transport     | scooter | trike    | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-6::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, photographer, musician
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, metal, techno
1. the musician is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the security-guard##5
3. the musician is somewhere to the right of the security-guard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Job         | photographer | security-guard | musician |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | metal   | techno        |

