.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-7::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, software-developer, teacher
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, train
1. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
2. the security-guard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
3. the software-developer is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |     2      |         3          |
| Job     | security-guard | teacher    | software-developer |
| Transport   | bus      | train | snowmobile             |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-8::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, azure, lavender
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, fisherman, pilot
1. the person who likes azure is on the left of the fisherman##1
2. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
3. the designer is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
4. the designer is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Color   | lavender | azure  | grey    |
| Job     | pilot   | designer | fisherman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, lemonade
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, trance, soul
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of soul is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage    | 7up       | coffee   | lemonade |
| Music-Genre   | trance | metal | soul  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-10::.
3 different games are played: poker, bridge, monopoly
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, reggae, salsa
1. the person playing monopoly is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the fan of house##5
3. the fan of house is between the fan of salsa and the fan of reggae##2
4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Game           | poker | bridge | monopoly |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | house      | salsa    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, mechanic, coach
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, chinese, indian
1. the chinese is on the right of the indian##1
2. the coach is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
3. the photographer is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job      | coach   | photographer     | mechanic      |
| Nationality   | indian | chinese | australian |

