.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-12::.
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, cauliflower, lettuce
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bolivar, havana
1. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the left of the havana-smoker##5
2. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person eating lettuce##5
3. the game-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating cabbage##5
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |    3    |
| Food        | cabbage | cauliflower | lettuce |
| Cigar   | bolivar  | game         | havana   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-13::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, pop, rock
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, mexican, malaysian
1. the pakistani is on the left of the mexican##1
2. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of pop##1
3. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the malaysian##5
4. the pakistani is on the left or right of the mexican##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | rock          | pop     | disco  |
| Nationality         | malaysian | pakistani | mexican |

