.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, water
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, police-officer, journalist
1. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
2. the journalist is on the right of the designer##1
3. the person drinking water is the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | water  | tea         |
| Job   | police-officer     | designer | journalist |

