.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-15::.
City: marseilles, prague, berlin
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
2. the person who's sport is basketball is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| City     | berlin | prague   | marseilles   |
| Sport   | badminton | basketball | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-16::.
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, corn, pear
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, sailing, snowboarding
1. the person eating pear is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
3. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating corn##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food   | pineapple | corn       | pear |
| Sport         | parkour | snowboarding | sailing |

